{
  "stem": "8212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I mean, the conditions there were absolutely terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to the commandant of this camp, and being that I was a child, he liberated my father, which means that we could go back to this village.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember walking from the camp to the next train station that was Elne in Les Pyrenees.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took a long time because my father was so weak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It took a long time to walk there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, finally, we took the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were absolutely magnificent peaches all over the place, and I wanted some, so my father bought me peaches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ate so many peaches that I got very sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we came back to this village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were told that we couldn't stay there, and we had to go to a camp, to a French camp, which was in Brens.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was called Brens, and it was in Albi, near Albi, where Toulouse-Lautrec comes from.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the way, during the night, we were taken to a prison, a real prison, to sleep over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no other place, which was also a very odd experience to be in a French prison.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From there, we went to that camp that had about 20 barracks, wooden barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Each barrack had about maybe 100 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were several layers of couchette where you slept.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the families were together, which was extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had a blanket, and there was a common place where you ate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the barrack just had one little oven in the middle that-- to heat the whole barracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The food was atrocious.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
